cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with visual perception for autonomous driving. It may also belong to Robotics (cs.RO) as it is related to autonomous driving. Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) are also likely sub-categories as the paper proposes a multi-task learning approach using a shared convolutional architecture.
